    <item>
      <title>文本显示，尽管爱泼斯坦有毒，史蒂夫·班农还是站在他一边</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/16/us/politics/jeffrey-epstein-steve-bannon.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[班农是 MAGA 播客，他与被指控性交易的杰弗里·爱泼斯坦 (Jeffrey Epstein) 建立了看似亲密的关系。他说这是为了让爱泼斯坦先生敞开心扉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/16/us/politics/jeffrey-epstein-steve-bannon.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Feb 2026 15:08:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
