    <item>
      <title>随着最新的回滚，美国基本上没有清洁汽车规则</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/16/climate/endangerment-finding-auto-emissions-regulations.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[专家表示，美国环保署取消了“危险发现”，这为一年的放松管制画上句号，这可能会使汽车对汽油更加渴求，并降低全球竞争力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/16/climate/endangerment-finding-auto-emissions-regulations.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Feb 2026 10:04:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
